These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, folk, r&b, reggae, soul
6 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, hedgehog, mouse, rabbit
 1. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of soul is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5
 3. the fan of reggae is not the owner of the mouse##6
 4. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5
 5. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 7. the owner of the mouse is not the fan of dubstep##6
 8. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of blues is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the fan of r&b##7
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
11. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
12. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
13. the owner of the cat is the fan of blues##1
14. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the fan of reggae##5
15. the fan of soul is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | blues | folk   | soul     | dubstep    | reggae   |
| Pet           | mouse | cat   | rabbit | hedgehog | guinea-pig | goldfish |

