.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: disaster, documentary, drama, fantasy, horror, time-travel
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, fish, guinea-pig, mouse, snake
 1. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
 2. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
 4. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 7. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
 8. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching horror movies is not the owner of the mouse##6
10. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
11. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
12. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
13. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
14. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4
15. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
16. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
17. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the owner of the dog and the person watching horror movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | time-travel | fantasy | horror     | drama      | disaster |
| Pet           | dog         | fish        | mouse   | guinea-pig | chinchilla | snake    |

