.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, lemonade, soy-milk, tea, water
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, lacrosse, parkour, surfing, swimming
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 2. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
 5. the person drinking cola is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
10. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
11. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
13. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5
14. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | tea        | soy-milk | water    | cola    | lemonade | hot-chocolate |
| Sport      | basketball | surfing  | swimming | parkour | baseball | lacrosse      |

