The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: crime, drama, fantasy, horror, superhero, western
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 2. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 3. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is not the person drinking mirinda##6
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking mirinda##7
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking water##7
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking lemonade##7
10. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
13. the person watching fantasy movies is the person drinking lemonade##1
14. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
