 5. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
 6. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the rabbit and the person driving the boat##2
 7. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
 9. the owner of the dog is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
11. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
12. the person driving the tram is somewhere between the owner of the goldfish and the person driving the motorbike##7
13. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Pet         | dog   | rabbit | bird      | lizard | rat  | goldfish   |
| Transport   | train | trike  | motorbike | boat   | tram | skateboard |

