.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: camping, collecting, drawing, photography, traveling, video-games
The people have 6 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, fisherman, journalist, project-manager, scientist
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the fisherman##5
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere between the journalist and the dressmaker##7
 5. the scientist is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is the project-manager##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
 8. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 9. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5
10. the dressmaker is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
11. the scientist is on the right of the fisherman##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
14. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
15. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Hobby   | drawing         | photography | collecting | camping   | video-games | traveling  |
| Job     | project-manager | journalist  | fisherman  | scientist | dressmaker  | accountant |

